videos.description: Ja Morant launches an alley-oop pass to KJ Williams from halfcourt, and Williams finishes it off with a strong two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Morant throws half-court alley-oop to Williams

videos.description: Ja Morant picks Josiah Wallace's pocket, then electrifies the crowd with a ridiculous one-handed windmill dunk to extend the Racers' lead late in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Morant hammers down crazy windmill dunk) 2019/02/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morant hammers down crazy windmill dunk

videos.description: Ja Morant hits four 3-pointers to start the game and throws down a nasty windmill dunk as a part of his 23-point night in Murray State's win.
